 40?pWVJfzw9XmZBk37o1Dm) Meeting ID: 294 167 537 955 140 Passcode: kG6qS7pm
  Dial in by phone 1 941-263-1615\,\,700525838 (tel:19412631615\,\,70052583
 8) United States\, Sarasota Find a local number (https:dialin.teams.micros
 oft.com4512eb87-edac-469e-b2a6-3809849d8bff?id700525838) Phone conference 
 ID: 700 525 838 AMERICANS WITH DISABILITIES ACT (ADA) Persons with disabil
 ities who need an accommodation in order to participate in this meeting sh
 ould contact the City of Tampa at least forty-eight (48) hours in advance 
 of the meeting. ADDITIONAL INFORMATION: For additional information regardi
 ng this public meeting\, please contact Amanda Alfarah at 813-274-5642. \n
